Package: fssetup
Title: Package for Producing R Projects and Scripts Using the Defra Farming Stats Template
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person(given = "Josh",
                  family = "Moatt",
                  email = "joshua.moatt@defra.gov.uk",
                  role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: This package contains the functions needed to create various features
 in R using the Defra Farming Stats Team templates. Including scripts, projects, readmes and
 gitignores. It also contains useful functions for linking RStudio and RStudio projects to
 GitHub. 
